--[[--------------------------< P R E P R I N T S U P P O R T E D P A R A M E T E R S >--------------------
Cite arXiv, cite biorxiv, cite citeseerx, cite medrxiv, and cite ssrn are preprint templates that use the limited set of parameters defined in the limited_basic_arguments and limited_numbered_arguments tables. Those lists are supplemented with a template-specific list of parameters that are required by the particular template and may be exclusive to one of the preprint templates. Some of these parameters may also be available to the general cs1|2 templates.
Same conventions for true/false/tracked/nil as above.
]]
